docs {
  # Cancel Order Notification - OpenAccess

  Provider notification steps for the Cancel Order journey per OA provider.

  - **ACES/** — Received → Accepted → InProgress → Cancelled
  - **ITC/** — Create Task → Assigned → Accepted → Set Off → Failure
  - **STC/** — Wait SSN ONT → Test FTTH Link → InProgress → Cancelled → Closed
}

